allorsUnifiedGood.name: STILL R07-25
allorsUnifiedGood.description:
- Pure concentrated force: R 07 tow and transport loads of up to 25 tons.
- Robust tractors are particularly impressive when used for luggage transit at airports and train stations.
- By coupling several trailers, the transport volume can be adjusted to suit any application, while the maintenance-free 80-volt three-phase motor guarantees powerful acceleration and an excellent ability to overcome ramps at a maximum speed of up to 25 km / h.
- Quick and safe trailer coupling thanks to the clear view of the trailer hitch
- Precision at the touch of a button: the reverse gear allows you to drive the tractor safely and precision to the trailer
- Sensitive acceleration and handling ensure that goods are transported safely and smoothly
